# Styling: Material Tokens + SCSS

- Use Angular Material v3 token override APIs for theming.
- Do not style Material internals with ad-hoc `.mat-*` / `.mdc-*` overrides.
- Use SCSS mixins/utilities for component styling and typography conventions.
- Use project typography mixins; avoid hardcoded `font-size`, `line-height`, and `font-weight`.
- Do not use Tailwind classes or propose Tailwind-first solutions in this project.

## Practical Guidance

- Prefer token-level changes in `theme.scss`.
- If token APIs are insufficient, use minimal scoped overrides and document why.
